http://www.cpac.org:80/nationalreview/26feb96/week.html 204.71.237.74 19970108164805 text/html 12158
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Wednesday, 08-Jan-97 16:48:22 GMT
