http://www.cpac.org:80/nationalreview/16jan96/week.htm 204.71.237.74 19970108164956 text/html 10368
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Wednesday, 08-Jan-97 16:50:06 GMT
Last-modified: Tuesday, 16-Jan-96 17:38:24 GMT
