<DOCNO>WT19-B23-70</DOCNO>
<DOCOLDNO>IA025-000260-B017-168</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://www.cpac.org:80/nationalreview/06nov95/week.htm 204.71.237.74 19970108165457 text/html 12492
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Wednesday, 08-Jan-97 16:55:09 GMT
Last-modified: Monday, 18-Dec-95 21:09:48 GMT
Content-length: 12305
