http://www.cpac.org:80/nationalreview/11sep95/week.htm 204.71.237.74 19970108165849 text/html 11266
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Wednesday, 08-Jan-97 16:59:04 GMT
Last-modified: Monday, 18-Dec-95 21:09:46 GMT
