http://www.cpac.org:80/nationalreview/21july95/lowry.htm 204.71.237.74 19970108170407 text/html 11152
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Wednesday, 08-Jan-97 17:04:14 GMT
