<p>

<h4>GARY L. BAUER RECOGNIZED AS AUTHORITATIVE
SPOKESMAN  FOR PRO-LIFE AMERICA TODAY IN <i>NEW YORK TIMES,
WASHINGTON POST</i>, AND OTHER MAJOR MEDIA</h4></center>

<br><p>

<h4>REASONS WHY LIFE ISSUE A MUST FOR POLITICAL COVERAGE THIS 
WEEK:</h4>

<p>
<li>Pro-life candidates win all three primaries -- Georgia, Kansas
and Michigan.

<p>

<li>These included:

<p><ul>

-- the fight for Dole's senate seat<br>
-- the Speaker's home state<br>
-- the state of a governor who has been on the short list of
Vice Presidential candidates

</ul><p>

